<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>Bromunity – Find Your Player Two</title>
  <style>
    * {
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      box-sizing: border-box;
    }

    body {
      font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'SF Pro Display', 'SF Pro Text', system-ui, sans-serif;
      background: #fafafa;
      color: #1a1a1a;
      line-height: 1.6;
      padding: 3rem 1.5rem;
      min-height: 100vh;
    }

    .container {
      max-width: 420px;
      margin: 0 auto;
    }

    .logo {
      font-size: 1.75rem;
      font-weight: 300;
      color: #2d5a3d;
      text-align: center;
      margin-bottom: 4rem;
      letter-spacing: 2px;
    }

    .hero {
      text-align: center;
      margin-bottom: 4rem;
    }

    .hero h1 {
      font-size: 2.25rem;
      font-weight: 200;
      color: #1a1a1a;
      margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
      line-height: 1.2;
    }

    .hero p {
      font-size: 1.1rem;
      color: #666;
      margin-bottom: 3rem;
      font-weight: 300;
    }

    .btn {
      background: #2d5a3d;
      color: white;
      border: none;
      padding: 1rem 2rem;
      border-radius: 25px;
      font-size: 1rem;
      font-weight: 400;
      cursor: pointer;
      transition: all 0.2s ease;
      letter-spacing: 0.5px;
    }

    .btn:hover {
      background: #234a30;
      transform: translateY(-1px);
    }

    .features {
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      gap: 1.5rem;
      margin-bottom: 4rem;
    }

    .feature {
      background: #ffffff;
      padding: 2rem;
      border-radius: 24px;
      border: 1px solid #e2e8f0;
      box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.04);
    }

    .feature h3 {
      font-size: 1.1rem;
      font-weight: 500;
      color: #2d5a3d;
      margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
    }

    .feature p {
      font-size: 0.95rem;
      color: #666;
      font-weight: 300;
    }

    .footer {
      text-align: center;
      color: #999;
      font-size: 0.85rem;
      font-weight: 300;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="logo">BROMUNITY</div>
    
    <div class="hero">
      <h1>Find Your Player Two</h1>
      <p>Connect with like-minded gamers for genuine friendships and epic gaming sessions.</p>
      <button class="btn">Join the Community</button>
    </div>

  <section>
    <div class="features">
      <div class="feature">
        <h3>Game Together</h3>
        <p>Find teammates who share your passion and gaming style.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="feature">
        <h3>Genuine Connections</h3>
        <p>Build real friendships beyond the screen.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="feature">
        <h3>Positive Vibes</h3>
        <p>A welcoming space focused on good times and respect.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

    <div class="footer">
      <p>© 2025 Bromunity</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
